    "long_instructions": "## **Refine Prompts to Mitigate Bias**\r\n\r\n1. Choose one of your original prompts from Level 1 and rewrite it to include a **specific group, style, or context**.\r\n\r\n\t**Examples:**\r\n    * \"Recommend 5 foods\" → \"Recommend 5 traditional Filipino foods\"\r\n    * \"Recommend 5 hairstyles\" → \"Recommend 5 protective hairstyles for curly hair\"\r\n    * \"Recommend 5 games\" → \"Recommend 5 games that don't need a lot of equipment\"\r\n    * \"Recommend 5 clothing styles\" → \"Recommend 5 modest clothing styles for teen girls\"\r\n2. Ask the refined version of the prompt in AI Chat.\r\n3. Note in your activity guide:\r\n\r\n\t* How it is different from the original?\r\n\t* Observed bias or patterns\r\n\t* What might still be missing?"
